      • doImport

        protected void doImport(Polyad polyad,
                        State state)
        The general contract for import. You may import everything in a module by using the uri. You may import items using the FQ name (uri + # + name).

        Imported items are added to the current stack only. it is nto possible to un-import items since it is impossible to track down references to them and it is dangerous to have programs be able to unload things willy-nilly since that can cause hard to track down failures.
        Parameters:
        polyad -
